data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY JANUARY 28th from 12:00 to 2:00. Welcome to your peaceful retreat! Located in Twin Lakes Community this gem is a 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a master bathroom, a kitchen that's a dream for those who love to cook, an in-house laundry room, and a generous outdoor space.  This home is located on a peaceful, family-friendly street. It's an ideal choice for families and those who appreciate the tranquility of a quiet neighborhood. HOA fees include Lawn care, HOA-owned pavilion a BBQ Grill, and lake with a fishing pier. Don't miss your chance to make this your forever home! Contact me today for a viewing
